Sheet47.Name: Crowd Control
Sheet47.Description: This means effects like sleep petrify stop which take the target out of play for a few turns

Sheet47.Name: Status Ailments
Sheet47.Description: these are effects like paralyze stun or delay which impact an enemy or player ability but allow them to still perform other actions

Sheet47.Name: Buffs
Sheet47.Description: These are abilities that boost specific stats of the targeted party

Sheet47.Name: Debuffs
Sheet47.Description: These are abilities that reduce specific stats of the targeted party

Sheet47.Name: Extreme Extra
Sheet47.Description: Extreme Extra - A much harder version of the extra stages with much harder conditions and enemies

Sheet47.Name: Job Mastery
Sheet47.Description: JobLv11 / Triggers Master Bonus

Sheet47.Name: Master Bonus
Sheet47.Description: Provides units with additional bonus stat percentages based on job mastered these stat bonuses carry over into other jobs

Sheet47.Name: Limit Break
Sheet47.Description: a seperate system which increases unit max level and combo count based on additional shards used

Sheet47.Name: Combo
Sheet47.Description: A stat which increases the probabilty and range of a combo attack this stat can be increased by limit breaking to a maximum of 32

Sheet47.Name: Combo Attack
Sheet47.Description: an attack which draws from comboed units to increase normal attack power

Sheet47.Name: Soul shards
Sheet47.Description: Currency required to limit break and transmute a unit

Sheet47.Name: Health/Hit Points
Sheet47.Description: Pool of damage that can be taken before a unit is out of play

Sheet47.Name: Physical Atk
Sheet47.Description: Increases power of physical attacks against targer

Sheet47.Name: Physical Def
Sheet47.Description: Decreases damage from physical attacks against unit

Sheet47.Name: Magic Atk
Sheet47.Description: Increases power of magic attacks against target

Sheet47.Name: Magic Def
Sheet47.Description: Decreases damage from magical attacks against unit

Sheet47.Name: Dexterity
Sheet47.Description: Influences attack (for certain classes) and hit rate

Sheet47.Name: Agility
Sheet47.Description: Determines the delay between unit turn

Sheet47.Name: Critical
Sheet47.Description: Affects Critical Hit Rate

Sheet47.Name: Luck
Sheet47.Description: Affects Luck Based Actions

Sheet47.Name: Combo
Sheet47.Description: Affects Combo Chance

Sheet47.Name: Move
Sheet47.Description: Range of a units Lateral Movement

Sheet47.Name: Jump
Sheet47.Description: Range of a units Vertical Movement

Small percentage of bonus stats added upon Job Mastering. These are carried over to other jobs.
Used for limit breaks. Collecting enough soul shards allows you to transmute the corresponding unit.
Extended collaboration with Dragon Genesis. Units released are referenced as DG# with # being the chronology they were released
Extra stage that extends above the normal events. Generally includes Materials Drops for Job Changes or Gears
A harder version of the Extra stage
Switching Job of a unit.
[Job Change] A Unique Job Upgrade to a unit. Comes with Events.
[Job Change] A Generic Job Upgrade to a unit. Available at all time.
Leveling a Job to level 11 and fully equipping that level. Adds [Job Master Bonus]
A seperate system which increases unit max level and combo count based on additional shards used
[LimitBreak] Limit breaking beyond lv85 by enlightenment  (Shinri Kaigan - Enlightenment of the Truth)
An effect on a unit that affects them positively.
An effect on a unit that affects them negatively.
A modification of a unit's state. [See Status Aliment Category]
Effects that prevent the use of abilities and actions
A unit's vital power. At 0 HP, a unit will get knocked out.
Attack power of physical attacks
Defensive power against physical attacks
Increases power of magic attacks against target
Defensive power against magical attacks
Influences attack power (for missile / projectile based jobs) and hit rate
Determines the rate of units getting their turns (Higher SPD increase CT more per Unit Time)
Charge time is used to determine when will the unit get their turn, at 100 CT, a unit will get their turn and will be able to act. (Not to be confused with cast time)
Spell with cast time require time before casting. (Not to be confused with Charge Time.)
Amount of additonal damage when inflicting a critical hit
Luck based stat, used as a stat for damage for specfic skills
[Aka. Chaining / Cooperation] Affects Combo Chance
Range of a units Vertical Movement
Range of a units Lateral Movement
Affects hit rate
Affects the rate a unit will cause [Miss] to incoming attacks [Can be added from Leader Skills / Passive]
Available only in the form of Reactive, Fixed chance to [Avoid] an attack. (Attack with Sure-Hit property can still be [Avoided])
Prevent Negative Status Aliment on effected unit for a certain amount of turns, also cure existing status aliment. (Unless the aliment is cursed.)
Unable to move or act. Effect ends when attacked.
Regain certain percentage of HP every turn.
Regain certain amount of Jewel every turn. (Amount based on skill or items)
3 Turn tick down for a unit, when the timer reaches zero, the unit is instantly defeated.
Deal Percentage HP damage to effected target unit. (The percentage can be increased using some passive.)
Decrease Accuracy and Dodge of a unit.
PATK UP and PDEF DOWN, Automatically attack nearby enemy.
Effected unit will only attack the one that inflicted the status effect.
Effected unit will normal attack ally unit. Effect ends when attacked. (They will not attack ally that are charmed.)
Effected unit will be unable to act or move indefinitely until cured.
Disable reactive and interrupt casting. (If the stun lasts more than 1 turn, it stops the unit from acting)
Effected unit will have a set chance of automatically ending their turn. Also reduces chances of reactive occurring
Set the MOV of effected unit to 1.
Prevent movement of effected unit. (Can use skill.)
Prevent normal attack and usage of skills that will deal damage to the enemy. (Heals/Buff/Debuff that deal no damage can be used.)
Prevents using skills and disable reactive. (Can still normal attack)
Prevents the generation of CT for certain amount of time, also disable Reactive and Dodge on the Unit. (35 Unit Time)
Decrease the generation of CT by 50% for a certain amount of time, effects casting (35 Unit Time)
Increase the generation of CT by 50% for a cetain amount of time, effects casting (35 Unit Time)

memcardnensou.lore:
この日お嬢様は、屋敷の地下室で見つけた古き本を片手に、埃を被っていた武器と出会ってしまったのです。
「これよ！　私が求めていた世界は！」
爛々と輝く瞳。興奮で上ずる声。その姿を見て、我々使用人は震えました。旦那様、奥様…、申し訳ございません。ローザお嬢様の人生は、この瞬間に様変わりしてしまったのかもしれません。（執事ワイアットの綴った手紙）
